{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"SYYEQDx0b8EddBehDADxU","title":"影视剧","desc":"","updated":1645157740064,"created":1645157542204,"custom":{},"fname":"censorship.subjects.moviestv","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"a15c00b173b1c9c901d1b7d1feb6905d","links":[{"from":{"fname":"censorship.tampering","id":"L1u0uhTXBNnCpe8cefRjS","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":8,"offset":8},"end":{"line":2,"column":43,"offset":43},"indent":[]},"value":"censorship.subjects.moviestv"}],"anchors":{"影视剧的引入和内容审查":{"type":"header","text":"影视剧的引入和内容审查","value":"影视剧的引入和内容审查","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2},"对影视剧的评分":{"type":"header","text":"对影视剧的评分","value":"对影视剧的评分","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2},"参考资料":{"type":"header","text":"参考资料","value":"参考资料","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"qA1wOFHTdkOq8ns8pAiwT","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"影视剧\">影视剧<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#影视剧\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"影视剧的引入和内容审查\">影视剧的引入和内容审查<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#影视剧的引入和内容审查\"></a></h2>\n<p>腾讯修改《搏击俱乐部》等电影。</p>\n<p>《老友记》重返中国最知名的流媒体服务平台，但一些剧情出现了重大改动。剧中角色罗斯的前妻是同性恋的情节被删除，其他几处涉及性的部分也遭到篡改。这些举动引发了许多粉丝的尖刻评论，他们表示改动强化了性别刻板印象。这也表明中国审查人员对娱乐行业有多么强大的掌控力。《老友记》在中国大陆流媒体新上线的版本里被删除了有关同性恋的台词和剧情。剧中罗斯的前妻卡罗尔的扮演者珍妮·希伯特（Jane Sibbett）得知此事后在Instagram上表达遗憾。</p>\n<h2 id=\"对影视剧的评分\">对影视剧的评分<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#对影视剧的评分\"></a></h2>\n<p>2021年全国电影工作会上，中宣部常务副部长、国家电影局局长王晓晖表示，今年要健全完善电影评价评估体系，构建起政治性艺术性相统一、社会反映和市场认可度相统一的电影作品评估机制。(<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/663290.html\">https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/663290.html</a>)</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考资料\">参考资料<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#参考资料\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/671646.html?utm_source=dlvr.it&#x26;utm_medium=twitter\">粗制滥造的主旋律，到底献给谁看？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/678251.html\">“说不完的八卦”：中国影视审查进化史</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/L1u0uhTXBNnCpe8cefRjS\">篡改</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","title":"墙国地图","desc":"","updated":1646712715590,"created":1644382378522,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"02c3c0c9e63ff90b668e6396d3f28d2a","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"underlying","alias":"实现方法","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":3,"offset":213},"end":{"line":12,"column":22,"offset":232},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"underlying"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"underlying","alias":"开源工具","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":3,"offset":382},"end":{"line":15,"column":24,"offset":403},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"underlying"}}],"anchors":{"如何使用审查地图":{"type":"header","text":"如何使用审查地图","value":"如何使用审查地图","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["vJRHPlmEzy8aoLmJq2EoS","qAItL5nac0TIpD7Uv7eB5","lFNqSJwuUdJJM9syQlMLP","4s98naE7Vp8rLwaBGAoRU","9mBvciCymZgzfdO2sVbde","EW05BFjl1ivR37Yv0wBIM","rTDV3gbrzSF4qbFVVLaPk"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n![](/assets/images/logo.png)\n\n墙国地图是社群共同贡献和维护的开源项目，目的是保存中国审查体系的来龙去脉，审查影响到的方方面面，人们的反制以及各种相关联的事件。\n\n因为采用了一种开放设计的机制，这个地图的版本将不断迭代并随时向贡献者发放特别的激励，所以你也可以加入并成为其中的一部分。\n\n## 如何使用审查地图\n\n审查地图是一个开源项目，你可以按图索骥，也可以补充完善，或者与更多人分享。\n\n- [[实现方法|underlying]]     \n- [源代码](https://github.com/China-Digital-Times-CDT/censorshipgraph)\n- [讨论](https://github.com/China-Digital-Times-CDT/censorshipgraph/issues)\n- [[开源工具 | underlying]]\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smar